{"tid":1468072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂］ 究竟邊個搞成今日咁","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:14.000Z","uid":147692,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"11940d0e304f9e2a94d361536b0bff81971ad710","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"咪就係坐喺度睇緊post嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家</span></span>囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇吓今日有幾多人 <br />\n琴日10份1都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想班手足點呀<br />\n口口聲聲話要癱機場<br />\n人呢？大佬呀，你要成功都要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">粒核彈呢？</span></span><br />\n又話核彈都唔放，我喺現場睇住啲post成個人灰哂<br />\n唔係要割蓆，但希望大家都可以體諒下手足。<br />\n我哋冇大台，全部嘢都係即場決定。<br />\n你唔滿意一齊親身去討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今日一戰，小弟認為有幾點不足之外：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.文宣不足 </span></span><br />\n要成功，就要全部手足同心合力，一齊出！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.前線手足要冷靜下先</span></span><br />\n絕非割蓆，但我哋都係打緊輿論戰，盡量可以都唔好俾人有位入！冷靜少少，我明大家都好大壓力，但有事上嚟唔好太激動住！諗諗先！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3.人少可以試吓考慮人流管制</span></span>　<br />\n人少就預咗啦，既然封depatures有咁大反應，不如試吓每個航空公司淨係比佢開一條登機位，得民心之餘又可以拖時間，最後結果都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4.唔好內控</span></span><br />\n大家有唔同意見好正常，冇話邊個啱邊個錯，尊重咁多位手足嘅意見，唔好啲狗未出手我哋就自己內控，我係狗睇住直播都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">5.用其他語言口號</span></span><br />\n喺機場嗌就係要話比其他國家嘅人聽而家發生咗啲咩事，繼續用廣東話帶佢哋都唔知我地講緊啲咩，所以試吓用其他語言表達下！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住一早講咗放核彈都唔割 唔好咁小事就即刻割晒蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做</span></span>"},{"pid":"27150ab008d5be497936ff939188e700800532b6","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"記著機場係政府春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3391f2bd51d4f6287ca83490d019e281d84b2f","tid":1468072,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b85e3706dc68b0566e7cfbb9be2972551b82dee3","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"我哋仲揸緊一手好牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba06264ab5e2eb6a0b64b7fd095e2268ddca5b6","tid":1468072,"uid":21609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12befcf404d12272e9c1c2d5a75fb007c9d5f586","tid":1468072,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"係政府"},{"pid":"b4c80a08b37c4249a5efaf4ccd6fbced5cc13e89","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 都夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24f824a0830209be6fb2e2b924ad07ab5c65aff","tid":1468072,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:53.000Z","msg":"戇鳩，搞成今日咁既係公安同黑警囉，我地和理非一向出名友好，絕對係d 狗狗混入示威者到搞事"},{"pid":"affed7781f52c4