a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Court 出左injunction ，聽日仲入去既，自己睇路，<br />\n林鄭就係想拎&ldquo;<ins>法庭授權警察清機場&rdquo;</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"4d8b355bd2846601ac1a8e232ccef0a74379da5b","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4380e9c41bf234634e3370057d409d0f7a0e7c","tid":1468072,"uid":188078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"根本今日大部分係和理非，數量一定係少左，但已經夠阻住機場運作唔到<br />\n日日都昨日咁多人仲辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"太多分化撚喺度屌手足 依家就係冇人 又冇大台 點癱機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b5b5a591b64e5ba8dedc648bf834dbe3f8fd65","tid":1468072,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhjRrXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhjRrXr.jpg&h=f0df7271&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbe372662b6e1e87c5dd769c0a14d28faf3ffb96","tid":1468072,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"成班人話現場比人煽動 好蠢<br />\n點知自己上個網都可以比五毛撚返轉頭"},{"pid":"e0c22b158eb13bd9cbd6e689ac75628d755cceff","tid":1468072,"uid":147692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc32ee6c1e0fe89bb2a069698aab50c64c6b4c3","tid":1468072,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">事實就係今日都係贏<br />\n成個運動拖一日就會多一日比共產黨同港共既壓力<br />\n唔好比支那五毛打擊士氣!!!!!<br />\n港共中共同五毛既目標係消滅抗爭<br />\n佢地做法就係製造內亂打擊士氣<br />\n只要唔好自己放棄就可以玩落去<br />\n多一日贏一日 又成最大贏家了!!!!</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"啱 放核彈都唔割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通一日及得上黑警做咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d03c22cd1d1678c7356564fd7b240d06a0a4e6